ar√° que cuando sea de d√≠a se active el light theme y cuando sea de noche se active el dark theme autom√°ticamente üòâ</p>\n<p>Eso es todo üéâ</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Si usas Windows puedes usar la extensi√≥n <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=danielgjackson.auto-dark-mode-windows\">Toggle Light/Dark Theme</a></p>\n</blockquote>","excerpt":"Hola üëã en este post vamos a ver una caracter√≠stica ch√©vere de VS Code con la cual se puede cambiar autom√°ticamente el tema que tengas de‚Ä¶","fields":{"slug":"/auto-dark-mode-en-vscode/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Auto dark mode en VSCode","date":"March 21, 2020","tags":["vscode","macOS"],"description":null,"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":150,"height":150,"src":"/static/43b0e32dbc26e7a02506a5c6aabd8d7a/92ab1/vsc.png","srcSet":"/static/43b0e32dbc26e7a02506a5c6aabd8d7a/92ab1/vsc.png 1x"}}},"banner":null,"slug":"auto-dark-mode-en-vscode"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/auto-dark-mode-en-vscode/","previous":{"id":"9687668f-5aba-511c-a3a9-4696b6754dcf","frontmatter":{"title":"C√≥mo formatear en macOS desde la terminal","tags":["macOS","terminal","format"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/como-formatear-en-mac-os-desde-la-terminal/"}},"next":{"id":"17f900c9-f63b-5c3b-af66-279c06716c01","frontmatter":{"title":"Generar un post a partir de un template con Hygen en Gatsby","tags":["hygen","gatsby"],"template":"post"},"fields":{"slug":"/generar-un-post-a-partir-de-un-template-con-hygen/"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}